Investing in Grocery-Anchored Shopping Centers


Scroll to see more information



Phillips Edison Grocery Center REIT II, Inc. (”Grocery Center REIT II”) is a publicly registered non-traded real estate investment trust

We seek to invest primarily in grocery-anchored neighborhood shopping centers with the following characteristics:

Occupied by a strategic mix of national and regional credit tenants
Focused on selling necessity-based goods and services
Located in strong demographic markets throughout the United States  


