Investing in Grocery-Anchored Shopping Centers 
THIS OFFERING IS CLOSED TO NEW INVESTMENTS. 
Phillips Edison Grocery Center REIT II, Inc. ("Grocery Center REIT II") is a publicly registered non-traded real estate investment trust* which seeks to invest primarily in grocery-anchored neighborhood shopping centers with the following characteristics:

Occupied by a strategic mix of national and regional credit tenants 
Focused on selling necessity-based goods and services 
Located in strong demographic markets throughout the United States  

Update on Status of our Transfer Agent: 
We are pleased to announce that DST Systems, Inc. has taken over as our new transfer agent. DST is now able to process account modification forms and take phone calls. New forms are available on the Investor Relations section of our website. We appreciate your patience and understanding as we have worked through this transition. 
